name: Interdependent
description:
Don't touch the wrong color! 

A short game created in 6 days for the 3rd Gdevelop Game Jam. 

Controls:

Left/Right key to move       F to separate yourself      Up key to interact

Credits: music made by Willibab: https://willibab.itch.io/willibabs-simple-8-bit-music

You can also play the game here: https://liluo.io/justanoctopus8/interdependent
